Global Understanding in Multilingual, Multimodal and Multimedia contexts (G=
UM3)
=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=
