Social Events
The timing of the conference will coincide with The Bryn Terfel Gala and=20
participants will be able to enjoy the evening concerts at this=20
internationally renowned festival. See http://www.brynfest.com for more det=
ails.

Travel and Accommodation
Good quality accommodation is available at a reasonable Price at Bangor=20
University either at the Business Management Centre or at the Halls of=20
Residence. All rooms are en-suite and have Internet facilities etc.

Airports with Transport Links to Bangor
Both Liverpool and Manchester airports are within a 1.5 hour drive from=20
Bangor. London airports are also within reach and may be combined with rail=
=20
travel.

Bangor is located on the direct London to Holyhead railway line.

There is also the possibility of a shuttle bus for people coming in via=20
Manchester airport.

Dublin is also possible for people flying in - fast ferry is only 99 minute=
s=20
to Holyhead and a 20 minute ride to Bangor.


